Kordhinta degdegga ah ee dhacdada guud ee cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) ee ka jirta Midowga Yurub/ aagga dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, inta u dhaxaysa 1 Janaayo iyo 15 Maarso 2020
Tirada guud ee kiisaska cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay muujineysaa horumar la mid ah wadamada Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, taasoo xaqiijineysa in, in kasta oo ay ku jiraan marxalado kala duwan, masiibada COVID-19 ay si dhakhso leh ugu sii kordheyso wadamada oo dhan.
Taariikhda Talyaaniga ayaa muujineysa in wadamada, isbitaalada iyo adeegyada daryeelka degdegga ah ay u baahan yihiin inay isu diyaariyaan in ay la kulmaan heerar sare oo bukaanada qaba COVID-19 ah oo u baahan daryeel, gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah.
31-kii Diseembar 2019, waxaa lagu soo sheegay Wuhan, gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha, in ay ka dhacday cudur cudur neefsanaan oo aan la aqoon xaaladdiisa.
Bishii Janaayo 9, 2020, Xarunta ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in wakiilka masuulka ka ah uu yahay coronavirus cusub oo hadda loo yaqaan coronavirus 2 ee cudurka neefsashada daran ee daran (SARS-CoV-2).
Tan iyo markaas, cudurka ka dhashay cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ayaa loo magacaabay cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ilaa hadda, qiyaastii 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay leeyihiin xaalad fudud, taas oo ah cudurrada neefsashada oo leh ama aan lahayn neefta, kuwaas oo intooda badan ay bogsadaan.
Qiyaastii 14% kiisaska COVID-19 waxay keenaan xanuun daran oo u baahan isbitaal, halka 6% ka mid ah kiisaska kale ay horumariyaan nooc ka mid ah cudurka oo u baahan daryeel degdeg ah.
Dhimashada bukaanka isbitaalka ah ee COVID-19 waxay qiyaastii tahay 4%.
Daraasaddan waxaan ku qiimeynay horumarka heerarka COVID-19 ee ku soo kordha wadamada Midowga Yurub/Magaalada Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EU/EEA) iyo Boqortooyada Midowday (UK) waxaanan isbarbardhignay horumarka ka dhacay gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignaa tirada hadda jirta ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday iyo kuwa Talyaaniga ee 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka Midowga Yurub/ECE iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Shiinaha kadib, COVID-19 ayaa sii faafay, iyo xawaaraha cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 ee adduunka intiisa kale ayaa hadda raacaya tan dalkaas.
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, Agaasimaha Guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa sheegay in COVID-19 uu yahay masiibad.
Daabacaadda 5 March ee Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. waxay soo sheegeen kiisaskii ugu horreeyay ee COVID-19 ee la xaqiijiyay Yurub sida lagu qeexay WHO.
Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub, saddexda kiis ee ugu horreeya ee la xaqiijiyay ayaa waxaa soo sheegay Faransiiska 24ka Janaayo 2020 dadka ka soo laabtay Wuhan, gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Laga soo bilaabo 15 Maarso 2020, kiisaska COVID-19 ayaa laga helay mid kasta oo ka mid ah 30da dal ee Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday (UK) iyadoo laga soo xigtay 31kii Diseembar 2019 ilaa taariikhdaas, 39,768 kiis iyo 1,727 dhimasho ayaa la sheegay, oo ay ka mid yihiin 17,750 kiis iyo 1,441 dhimasho oo ku saabsan Talyaaniga oo keliya.
Hel tirada guud iyo tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19
Xarunta Yurub ee Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (CEPCM), tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee laga soo sheegay waddan kasta oo adduunka ah, oo laga helay oo keliya ilo rasmi ah sida wasaaradaha caafimaadka, maamulka caafimaadka ee wadamada iyo WHO, ayaa la cusbooneysiiyay maalin kasta 8 subaxnimo.
Macluumaadkan ayaa loo adeegsaday in lagu qiimeeyo isbeddellada COVID-19 ee Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, isla markaana la barbardhigo khibrada Talyaaniga.
Si loo qiimeeyo heerka cudurka COVID-19 ee firfircoon, waxaan xisaabinay 14 maalmood oo guud oo COVID-19 ah, iyadoo la tixgelinayo isbeddelka dabiiciga ah ee COVID-19 ee ku yaal waddan kasta oo Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, intii u dhaxaysay Janaayo 1 ilaa Maarso 15, 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignay tirada guud ee kiisaska laga soo sheegay waddan kasta 15 Maarso 2020 saacaddii 8 subaxnimo xogta Talyaaniga ee 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Isbeddelka COVID-19 ee dalalka Midowga Yurub/EES iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Dhacdada 14 maalmood ee COVID-19 ee ka dhacay wadamada Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa guud ahaan raacday tan gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha (Sawir 1).
Midowga Yurub/EES iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, tirada guud ee COVID-19 waxay bilaabeen inay koraan qiyaastii Febraayo 21 ka hor inta aysan kor u kacsan qiyaastii Febraayo 28, 2020 (macluumaad dheeri ah).
Horumarkan ayaa ugu horreyn sabab u ahaa kororka degdegga ah ee kiisaska laga soo sheegay Talyaaniga, laakiin dhammaan dalalka kale ee EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa muujiyay koror la mid ah dhacdada COVID-19 ee la isku daray (macluumaad dheeri ah).
Sawirka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee ka dhacay waddamada Midowga Yurub/Wadamada ETA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday marka loo eego xogta Talyaaniga ee taariikhda 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Waxaa la ogaaday in saacadii 8 subaxnimo ee 15ka Maarso 15 dal oo kale oo ka tirsan EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ay soo sheegeen tirada guud ee kiisaska la midka ah tii Talyaaniga oo kaliya 3 todobaad ka hor ama ka yar.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay muujinayaan in tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee la soo sheegay ay si degdeg ah u kordhayaan Midowga Yurub/EES iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Isbeddelka heerka guud ee COVID-19 wuxuu muujinayaa in cudurka faafa uu ku sii kordhayaa xawaare la mid ah dalalka oo dhan.
Taasi waa in kasta oo wadamada ay ku jiraan marxalado kala duwan oo ay jiraan kala duwanaansho ka jira jawaabaha adeegyada caafimaadka dadweynaha ee dalka, kala duwanaansho suurtagal ah oo ku saabsan qeexitaanka kiisaska iyo kala duwanaansho ku saabsan nidaamyada xulashada bukaanka ee loo baaro xaqiijinta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan baaritaanka soo kabashada.
Bilowgii bishii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiirta gobollada ay saameysay ee Talyaaniga ayaa sheegay in ku dhawaad 10% bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ay u baahan yihiin daryeel degdeg ah, warbaahinta ayaa sheegtay in isbitaalada iyo adeegyada daryeelka degdegga ah ee gobolladaasi ay horey u gaareen awoodooda ugu badan.
Xogta ku saabsan cusbitaalada iyo/ama rugta daryeelka degdegga ah ee COVID-19 ayaa hadda laga heli karaa EU/EEA oo dhan oo kaliya 6% iyo 1% kiisaska, siday u kala horreeyaan (Xogta aan la soo bandhigin).
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa lagama maarmaan ah in la sameeyo ururinta nidaamsan si loo dhammaystiro xogta kormeerka ee hadda jirta oo diiradda saaraya tirada kiisaska la soo sheegay iyo dhimashada.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay 201011 ayaa muujisay kala duwanaansho weyn oo ku saabsan tirada sariiraha laga heli karo adeegyada daryeelka dhexe iyo kuwa daran ee Yurub, laga bilaabo 29.2 sariirood halkii 100,000 qof ee Jarmalka ilaa 4.2 sariirood ee Portugal.
Taas macnaheedu waa in wadamada ay haystaan kheyraadyo ka yar ama ka badan kuwa Talyaaniga (12.5 sariirood oo daryeel degdeg ah iyo kuwa dhexdhexaad ah oo 100 000 qof ah sanadkii 201011).
Sawirada qaabeynta ee ku saabsan buuxinta awoodda daryeelka, oo leh qiyaaso ku saabsan waddan kasta oo Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ee ku saabsan heerka cudurka COVID-19 ee isbitaalka lagu xiro halis ah in 90 boqolkiiba ka badan awoodda sariirta daryeelka degdegga ah, waxaa lagu bixiyaa cusbooneysiinta lixaad ee qiimeynta degdegga ah ee COVID-19 ee CEPCM.
Maadaama kiisaska ay ilaa iyo hadda ku soo ururay gobollada qaar ka mid ah wadamada Midowga Yurub/Wadamada Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, isbitaalada iyo adeegyada daryeelka degdegga ahna ay caadi ahaan ku jiraan dad gobol ah oo la cayimay, xogta kiisaska iyo sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah waxaa ugu fiican in lagu soo saaro heerka 2 ee magacaabista cutubyada gobolka ee tirakoobka (NUTS 2).
Khibrada Talyaaniga iyo isbeddellada hadda ka jira dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in masiibada COVID-19 ay si dhakhso leh ugu sii kordheyso Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Wadamada, isbitaalada iyo adeegyada daryeelka degdegga ah waa in ay diyaar garoobaan xaaladda gudbinta bulshada ee joogtada ah ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo sidoo kale kororka tirada bukaanka qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel, gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah, sida gobollada ay saameysay Talyaaniga.
Sida lagu muujiyey qiimeynta khatarta ee dhawaan ee degdegga ah ee CEPCM, habka degdegga ah, horumarsan iyo dhammaystiran ayaa muhiim u ah in la daahiriyo faafitaanka SARS-COV-2, laga soo bilaabo habka ka hortagga ilaa habka yareynta, maadaama kororka degdegga ah ee hore ee tirada kiisaska aysan siin karin waqti ku filan go'aan-qaadayaasha iyo isbitaalada si ay u fahmaan, u aqbalaan oo ay ula qabsadaan jawaabtooda haddii aan horay loo hirgelin.
Qiimaynta khatarta degdegga ah waxay sidoo kale ku taxadartaa tallaabooyinka caafimaadka dadweynaha ee yareynta saameynta cudurka faafa.
Waxaa jira daaqad gaaban oo dal kasta uu ku xoojin karo dadaalkiisa xakamaynta si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 loona yareeyo cadaadiska adeegyada caafimaadka.
Haddii kale, nidaamyada caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee EU/EEA waxay u badan tahay inay la kulmi doonaan tiro sare oo bukaan ah oo u baahan daryeel degdeg ah maalmaha ama usbuucyada soo socda.
Faafafka cudurka Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), oo ay sababtay cudurka coronavirus 2 ee cudurka neefsashada daran ee SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2), ayaa ilaa iyo hadda sababay in ka badan 3,000 oo qof ay dhintaan, waxaana cudurka ku dhacay in ka badan 80,000 oo qof Shiinaha iyo meelo kale oo adduunka ah, taasoo sababtay masiibo bani'aadamnimo.
Sida SARS-CoV, oo sababay kumanaan kiis oo SARS ah sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 waxaa laga yaabaa in lagu faafiyo jiirka oo ay calaamado la mid ah ku keento hab la mid ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, COVID-19 waxay leedahay heerar ka yar oo daran iyo dhimashada sida SARS, laakiin waa mid aad u faafa, waxayna saameyn badan ku yeelataa dadka waayeelka ah marka loo eego dhalinyarada iyo ragga marka loo eego dumarka.
Marka la eego tirada daabacaadaha ee ku saabsan cudurkan soo ifbaxaya oo si degdeg ah u kordhaya, maqaalkani wuxuu ku dadaalaa inuu bixiyo aragti ku filan oo dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan mawduuca cilmi baarista ee soo koraya.
Waxaan ka hadli doonaa aasaaska cudurrada faafa, xaaladda cudurka, fayraska, cudurrada lagu ogaado, daaweynta, saadaasha iyo ka hortagga cudurka.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli su'aalo ka jiraan jawaabaha, waxaan rajeyneynaa in baaritaankan uu gacan ka geysan doono fahamka iyo baabi'inta cudurkaas daran.
Xaflada gu'ga ee 25ka Janaayo 2020 ayaa si joogto ah u calaamadeysay dadka Shiinaha, kuwaas oo lagu qasbay inay ku xirnaadaan toddobaadka oo dhan iyo toddobaadyada kale ee dheer sababtoo ah faafitaanka cudur cusub oo fayras ah.
Fayraska ayaa aad ugu eg coronavirus (CoV) oo sababeysa cudurka cudurka neefsashada ee daran ee SARS (SRAS) sanadkii 2003; taasina waa sababta ay ugu magac dartay SARS-CoV-2 Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) 11kii Febraayo 2020, cudurka la xiriira oo loo yaqaan cudurka coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay Wuhan wuxuuna si dhakhso leh ugu faafay Shiinaha oo dhan ka hor inta uusan u faafin ku dhowaad 50 dal oo kale oo adduunka ah.
Bishii Maarso 2, 2020, fayraska ayaa sababay in ka badan 80,000 oo kiis oo COVID-19 ah la xaqiijiyay, iyadoo in ka badan 40,000 oo bukaan ah la dhigay isbitaalka, in ka badan 3,000 oo qofna ay dhinteen.
WHO waxay sheegtay in COVID-19 ay tahay cadowga ugu weyn ee dadweynaha, taas oo khatar ka badan argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood, in ka badan 200 oo shaqo ayaa lagu daabacay COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan qaybaha fayraska, cudurrada faafa, xaaladda cimilada, cudurka lagu ogaado iyo daaweynta, tan iyo markii warbixinta ugu horeysay ee 7ka Janaayo 2020 ay soo bandhigtay taxanaha fayraska, oo ka go'doomay bukaanno badan.
Dib u eegistaani waxay isku daydaa inay soo koobto horumarka cilmi baarista ee ku saabsan mawduucan cusub ee soo koraya.
Sida ugu dhakhsaha badan ee suurtogalka ah, waxaan isku dayi doonaa inaan isbarbardhigno COVID-19 SARS iyo cudur kale oo coronavirus ah, cudurka neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, oo ah faafitaan ka dhacay 2012.)
Waxaan sidoo kale dib u eegeynaa waxa aan hadda ka baranay ka hortagga iyo saadaasha cudurka, waxaanan ka hadli doonaa qaar ka mid ah arrimaha weli la joogo laakiin aad u degdeg ah.
Coronavirus-ka waxaa caadi ahaan loo tixgeliyaa inay yihiin cudur-darrada aan u dhimanayn dadka, kuwaas oo inta badan keena 15% ka mid ah hargabka caadiga ah 4.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee qarnigii, waxaan aragnay laba cudur oo cudur-darrada ah oo aad u daran oo aadanaha ah, kuwaas oo ah SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, kuwaas oo keentay cudur-darrada ka bilaabatay Shiinaha 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya 2012 siday u kala horreeyaan, ka hor inta aysan si degdeg ah u faafin dalal kale oo badan oo leh cudur-darrada iyo dhimashada sare.
COVID-19-ka hadda jira ayaa ah cudurka saddexaad ee coronavirus ee taariikhda dhawaan.
Sida lagu muujiyey sawirka 1.1, cudurrada sanbabada ee asalka aan la ogeyn ayaa markii ugu horreysay laga soo sheegay Wuhan 31-kii Diseembar 2019 Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha.
Toddoba maalmood kadib, la shaaciyay sida uu u dhacay cudurka coronavirus.
Bishii Janaayo 15, 2020, kiiskii ugu horreeyay ee dhimashada ayaa laga soo sheegay Wuhan.
