Isticmaalka xogta goobta ee taleefanada gacanta ee dowladaha ayaa ka dhashay arrimo la xiriira asturnaanta, iyadoo Amnesty International iyo in ka badan 100 urur oo kale ay soo saareen warbixin ay ku baaqeen in la xakameeyo kormeerka noocan ah.
Codsiyada kala duwan ee mobilada ayaa la bilaabay ama la soo bandhigay iyadoo la adeegsanayo adeegyada iskaa wax u qabashada, iyo ilaa iyo 7 April 2020, in ka badan 12 kooxood oo khubaro ah ayaa ka shaqeynayay xalal asturnaanta ah, sida isticmaalka Bluetooth si loo diiwaangeliyo joogitaanka isticmaaleha ku dhow taleefannada kale ee gacanta.
Isticmaalayaasha ayaa markale helaan fariin haddii ay xiriir dhow la lahaayeen qof lagu xaqiijiyey inuu helay COVID-19. Fikradaha qaldan ayaa hadda ku baahsan sida looga hortago cudurka; tusaale ahaan, sanka iyo afka lagu maydho ma shaqeynayaan.
Ma jiro tallaal COVID-19, laakiin hay'ado badan ayaa hadda isku dayaya inay horumariyaan.
