Stephen Griffin oo ah cilmiga fayraska ee Jaamacadda Leeds ayaa sheegay in xirashada maaskaro ay yareyn karto dabeecada dadka ay ku taabtaan wajiga, taas oo ah ilo weyn oo cudurro ah marka aanay jirin nadaafad sax ah oo gacmaha.
