Qaar ka mid ah xeryaha hore loo oggolaaday daaweynta cudurrada kale ee fayraska ayaa hadda lagu daraasadaa daaweynta COVID-19.
WHO waxay sheegtay in daawooyinka dhaqameed iyo farsamada qaarkood ay yareyn karaan astaamaha ay keento SARS-CoV-19.
Kordhinta awoodda iyo hagaajinta daryeelka caafimaadka ee baahida bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ayaa WHO ku tilmaamay inay tahay tallaabo muhiim u ah jawaabta cudurka faafa.
LECDC iyo Xafiiska gobolka ee WHO ee Yurub waxay soo saareen tilmaamo ku saabsan isbitaalada iyo adeegyada daryeelka caafimaadka ee aasaasiga ah si loo soo celiyo khayraadka heerar kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan in la siiyo adeegyada shaybaarka baaritaanka COVID-19, in la joojiyo tallaabooyinka aan degdeg ahayn marka ay suurtagal tahay, in la kala saaro loona gooyo bukaannada COVID-19-ka ah, iyo in la xoojiyo awoodda daryeelka degdegga ah iyada oo loo marayo tababarka shaqaalaha iyo kordhinta tirada taageereyaasha iyo sariiraha la heli karo.
