Bilowgii iyo bartamihii Janaayo 2020 ayaa fayraska uu ku faafay gobollada kale ee Shiinaha, taas oo ay gacan ka geysteen socdaalka sanadka cusub ee Shiinaha iyo xaqiiqda ah in Wuhan ay tahay xarun gaadiid iyo sidoo kale goob weyn oo isbarbardhig tareen ah.
