Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M iyo Tony S), iyo kooxda kale ee maamulka (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M iyo Toby N).
bLenzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran wajiga dibadda (bararka unugyada) ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
LACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka laenzym ee beddelashada angiotensin (ACE) iyadoo la yareeyo qadarka dangiotensin II iyo kordhinta lAng (1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daroogada ah oo rajo leh daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. LACE2 ayaa sidoo kale ah meesha laga galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah cudurrada coronavirus.
Nooca aadanaha ee lenzyme waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Langiotensin 2 enzyme-ka beddelidda waa zinc-ka ku jira metalloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Protein ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay domain M2 oo ah peptidase N-terminal ah iyo domain C-terminal oo ah xamuulka xamuulka ee xamuulka ah ee neerfaha.
LACE2 waa borotiinka xajmiga leh ee nooca I, oo heerka enzymatic ee firfircoon uu ku muuqdo dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Aagga ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa ka soo saaray aagga transmembrane by enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase; borotiinka dhalata waxaa lagu sii daayaa dhiigga, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu soo saaraa urine.
LACE2 wuxuu ku jiraa xubnaha badankood: lACE2 wuxuu ku xiran yahay xajmiga unugyada inta badan unugyada nooca II ee unugyada sanbabada, unugyada qanjirka hoose ee unugyada, unugyada dhiigga iyo xididdada, iyo unugyada dhiigga ee muruqyada fudud ee xubnaha badankood.
Xogta RNAm ee ACE2 waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, striatum, hypothalamus iyo maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa in ay ka dhigto in ay ka badiso ACE.
LACE waxay u kala qaybiso angiotensin I hormoonka angiotensin II oo ah xididdada xididdada.
LACE2 waxay si kale u kala saartaa carboxyl-terminated amino acid phenylamine of angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) iyo hydrolysis of angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku dhajin kartaa dhowr peptide oo kale oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, iyo ghrelin.
LACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga membrane ee xamuulka amino acid neutral SLC6A19 waxayna ku lug leedahay cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protein', lACE2 waa meesha ugu weyn ee lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah cudurrada coronavirus, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska ka soo jeeda SARS) iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska ka soo jeeda COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirka borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ku jira xarunta enzymatic ee lACE2 ee ku saabsan dusha unugyada waxay keentaa lendocytosis iyo wareejinta labada fayraska iyo lenzyme ee ku jira unugyada gudaha.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in borotiinka S uu la soo dejiyo protease-ka serine ee TMPRSS2 ee hadda lagu baarayo in la joojiyo sida daaweynta suurtagalka ah, taas oo keentay in dadka qaar ay u maleynayaan in yareynta heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay gacan ka geysan karto la dagaalanka cudurka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, shirkado badan iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado daaweynta caadiga ah ee ACE inhibitor iyo ARB.
Dib u eegis taxane ah iyo falanqayn meta oo la daabacay 11 July 2012 ayaa muujisay in  isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay la xiriirtay hoos u dhac weyn oo 34% ah oo halista cudurka sanbabada marka loo eego dadka la xakameynayo. 
Intaa waxaa dheer, halista cudurka ' pneumonia ' ayaa sidoo kale hoos u dhacday bukaannada la daaweeyay ACE inhibitor oo halis u ah cudurka ' pneumonia ', gaar ahaan kuwa ku dhaca wadnaha iyo wadnaha.
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale la xiriiray hoos u dhac ku yimaada dhimashada cudurka sanbabada, inkastoo natiijooyinka ay ka yar yihiin halista guud ee cudurka sanbabada.
Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan ' human recombinant angiotensin 2 converting enzyme (rhACE2) ' ayaa loo maleynayaa inuu yahay daaweyn hal-abuurnimo leh oo lagu daaweynayo dhaawaca daran ee sanbabada waxaana la sheegay inuu hagaajinayo hawo-nafsiga sanbabada iyo oksijiin-sareynta ee doofaarka qaba cudurka lipopolysaccharide-ka ah ee neefsashada.
Nolosha nuska ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa qiyaastii 10 saacadood, waqtiga ficilkuna waa 30 daqiiqo oo dheeri ah marka lagu daro 24 saacadood oo saameyn ah.
Qaar ka mid ah natiijooyinka ayaa muujinaya in rhACE2 uu noqon karo daawo rajo leh dadka u dulqaadanaya xakameynta caadiga ah ee neerfaha neerfaha (RAS) ama cudurada qaba wareegga sare ee neerfaha II. RhACE2 infushinka ayaa lagu qiimeeyay tijaabooyinka bukaanka ee daaweynta cudurka neefsashada degdegga ah.
Codsiyada COVID-19 waa codsiyada mobilada ee loogu talagalay inay fududeeyaan raadinta xiriirka cudurka faafa ee 2019-20, taas oo ah in la aqoonsado dadka ( xiriirada ) ee la xiriira qof qaba cudurka.
Codsiyada kala duwan ayaa la sameeyay ama la soo jeediyay, iyadoo la taageerayo dowladda rasmiga ah ee gobollada iyo xukunka qaarkood.
Qaar ka mid ah kaabayaasha ayaa la sameeyay si loo qaabeeyo codsiyada raadraaca xiriirka.
Nidaamyadan, gaar ahaan kuwa ku saleysan raadinta goobta jawiga ee dadka isticmaala barnaamijyada, waxay keenaan su'aalo ku saabsan ixtiraamka asturnaanta.
