Australia iyo New Zealand waxay qorsheynayaan inay ku soo bandhigaan codsiyada lagu daydo TraceTogether ee Singapore iyo BlueTrace Protocol. Ruushka ayaa doonaya inuu soo bandhigo codsi lagu dayactiro dhulka bukaannada la ogaaday inay qabaan COVID-19 oo deggan Moscow si loo hubiyo in aysan guriga ka bixin.
Ross Anderson oo ah Professor injineernimada amniga ee Jaamacadda Cambridge ayaa tilmaamay dhibaatooyin badan oo la xiriira isticmaalka nidaamyada ku saleysan codsiyada, oo ay ku jiraan falcelin been abuur ah iyo waxtar la'aan suurtagal ah haddii codsiyada ay isticmaalaan qayb yar oo dadka ka mid ah.
