Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in lhydroxychloroquine uu leeyahay sifooyinka ka hortagga garaaca cytokine. tocilizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta ee gudiga caafimaadka ee Shiinaha kadib markii la sameeyay daraasad yar.
Waxaa lagu baarayaa heer qaran oo aan la kala soocin heerka 2aad ee Talyaaniga kadib markii uu natiijooyin wanaagsan ka helay dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Marka la isku daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee ferritin serum si loo ogaado argagaxa cytokine, waa in la hortagaa horumarkaas oo la maleynayo inay sabab u tahay dhimashada dadka qaarkood ee saameeyay.
Lleukin-6 receptor antagonist waxaa FDA ansixisay iyada oo loo marayo daraasadaha kiiska dib u eegista ee daaweynta cudurka cudurka cudurka loo yaqaan 'steroid-refractory cytokine relargement syndrome' ee sabab kale, daaweynta CAR T cells, sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo random ah oo la xakameynayo oo muujinaya in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CFS.
Wareejinta antibody-yada la isku halleynayo ee la nadiifiyo ee nidaamyada difaaca ee dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 loo wareejiyo dadka u baahan ayaa lagu baranayo sidii hab aan tallaal ahayn oo loo sameeyo tallaalka aan la tallaalin.
Istaraatijiyadani waxaa lagu tijaabiyey SARS natiijooyin yar oo la xaqiijiyay.
Neutralization virus waa habka la filayo ee lagu sameeyo daaweynta antibody-ka ee aan waxtar lahayn ee ka hortagga SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale oo sida cytotoxicity-ka unugyada ku tiirsan antibodies iyo/ ama phagocytosis ayaa suurtagal noqon kara.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibiyootigga ee aan waxtarka lahayn, tusaale ahaan iyadoo la adeegsanayo antibodies monoclonal oo la soo saaray, ayaa la horumarinayaa.
Soo saarista serum ee dadka soo kabashada ah, oo ka kooban qaybta dareeraha ah ee dhiigga bukaanka la bogsiiyay oo ay ku jiraan jirka ka hortagga fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo soo bandhigo si dhakhso leh.
